This is a "maven-ized" version of the Apache Mahout Tutorial originally published here ...

http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/java/library/j-mahout

To build it you need to install Maven 3 and run ...

> ./buildAll.sh

This will take a while (30-60 mins), because we need to download the test data.

Enjoy - roland@tritsch.org (Dec 2011)
